article_title: Singapore to ban 'The Kashmir Files'; says movie "beyond" classified guidelines
event: Under the film classification guidelines, “any material that is denigrating to racial or religious communities in Singapore” will be refused classification, the authorities added.

article_title: J&K to have 90 constituencies as delimitation panel orders come into effect
event: According to the orders of the commission, set up under the Jammu and Kashmir Reorganisation Act of 2019, the Union territory will have 90 assembly constituencies.
